  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Natural Selection
Formula: Favorable traits lead to greater reproduction
Note:    Mechanism of evolution; Darwin 1859

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   Conservation of Mass
Formula: Reactants mass = Products mass
Note:    Mass is conserved in all chemical reactions

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Central Limit Theorem
Formula: Sample means → normal distribution
Note:    Foundation of statistical inference and polling

Domain:  Medicine
Topic:   Human Genome
Formula: ~3 billion base pairs; ~20,000 genes
Note:    Completed Human Genome Project 2003

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Bayes Theorem
Formula: P(A|B) = P(B|A)P(A)/P(B)
Note:    Updating probability based on new evidence

